name: Toca Lab: Plants
summary: In Toca Lab: Plants you will experiment at each station to see how the plants evolve. Keep experimenting until you've collected all 35 plant characters in the app. Once you've collected a plant, keep experimenting to continue to evolve it! Who says kids can't be scientists? Toca Lab: Plants brings out the budding botanist in everybody!
